videos.description: Taylor Koenen deflects the entry pass and Paris Kea takes it the other way for the Tar Heels, crossing up Jordan Nixon for the fast-break finish.
videos.headline: UNC's Kea goes coast-to-coast for smooth finish

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale picks off the pass and pushes in transition, finding a streaking Marina Mabrey for the fast-break finish.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale steals, Mabrey scores

videos.description: Paris Kea gets into the lane and hits a leaning bank shot, then steals the inbounds pass and scores again to give the Tar Heels a 49-47 lead.
videos.headline: Kea puts UNC ahead with 4 points in 5 seconds

videos.description: Leah Church spots up from the corner and knocks down a clutch 3-ball to give the Tar Heels a 74-71 lead over the Fighting Irish.
videos.headline: UNC's Church hits go-ahead 3 with under a minute left

videos.description: Paris Kea scores a season-high 30 points to power North Carolina to a 78-73 win over No. 1 Notre Dame.
